messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Security Report

Thanks to the tireless efforts of our security and intelligence divisions, there are currently no credible threats to Festive Drydock Tau. All station construction projects have been authorized. Have a secure shift!

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Power Systems Nominal

All SMESs on Festive Drydock Tau have been recharged. We apologize for the inconvenience.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Power Systems Nominal

Power has been restored to Festive Drydock Tau. We apologize for the inconvenience.
